train <- window(AirPassengers, end=c(1959, 12))

データプロット

plot(train,type="o")

## 自己相関・偏自己相関

library(forecast)
ggtsdisplay(train)

# 対数変換

log_AirPassengers <- log(train)
plot(log_AirPassengers,type="o")

差分データの表示

diff_log_AirPassengers = diff(log_AirPassengers,lag=1)
plot(diff_log_AirPassengers)

## ARIMAモデルの構築

model.0 <- arima(log_AirPassengers,order = c(1,0,1))

残差の自己相関

tsdiag(model.0)

自動ARIMAモデルの構築

model.1 <- auto.arima(
    log_AirPassengers,
    ic="aic",
    trace=T,
    stepwise=F,
    approximation=F,
    start.p=0,
    start.q=0,
    start.P=0,
    start.Q=0
)
